cs.NI, cs.GT, cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.MM

The paper discusses the optimization of wireless communications with UAVs, which involves network infrastructure and communication protocols. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also extensively discusses game-theoretic approaches, which suggests that it could belong to cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). Additionally, the paper mentions optimization techniques, which could place it in cs.IT (Information Theory). Finally, the paper discusses the use of UAVs for video streaming, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia).
